        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Mental Health Research Accelerator Act of </strong><b>2023</b></p> <p>This bill allows a tax credit through 2033 for 25% of expenses for translational research regarding neurodegenerative diseases and psychiatric conditions. The credit amount is subject to limitations, including an aggregate national limitation of $1 billion in 2024, $2 billion in 2025-2028, and $1 billion in 2029.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
